{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":103,"Text":"他們倆既已順服真主，而他使他的兒子側臥著。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":104,"Text":"我喊叫說：「易卜拉欣啊！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":105,"Text":"你確已証實那個夢了。」我必定要這樣報酬行善的人們。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":106,"Text":"這確是明顯的考驗。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":107,"Text":"我以一個偉大的犧牲贖了他。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":108,"Text":"我使他的令名，永存於後代。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":109,"Text":"「祝易卜拉欣平安！」"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":110,"Text":"我要這樣報酬行善者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":111,"Text":"他確是我的信道的僕人，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":112,"Text":"我以將為先知和善人的易司哈格向他報喜。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":113,"Text":"我降福於他和易司哈格。他們倆的子孫中，將有行善者和公然自暴自棄者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":114,"Text":"我確已施恩於穆薩和哈倫。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":115,"Text":"我曾使他們倆及其宗族，得免於大難。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":116,"Text":"我曾援助他們，所以他們是勝利者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":117,"Text":"我授予他們倆詳明的經典，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":118,"Text":"我指引他們倆正直的道路，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":119,"Text":"我使他們倆的令名，永存於後代。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":120,"Text":"「祝穆薩和哈倫平安！」"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":121,"Text":"我必定要這樣報酬行善者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":122,"Text":"他們倆確是我的信道的僕人。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":123,"Text":"易勒雅斯確是使者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":124,"Text":"當時，他對他的宗族說：「難道你們不敬畏真主嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":125,"Text":"難道你們祈禱白耳利，而捨棄最優越的創造者——"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":126,"Text":"真主，你們的主，你們祖先的主嗎？」"}]}